{"tid":1215949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線報導期間獲年青示威者贈雨傘、頭盔 美國CBS台記者讚揚年青示威者友善","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:53:48.000Z","uid":150685,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa88d93539dcb0799345bc06fc6a67c9949db48a","tid":1215949,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201906/20190613155819_0_cbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201906%2F20190613155819_0_cbs.jpg&h=fba2d4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCBS電視台駐亞洲記者Ramy Inocencio(英若明)昨日在金鐘進行採訪，於警方開始出動武力制止示威者後，不少示威者都慌忙走避，Ramy Inocencio與攝影師一同作前線報導，他指當時警方發射催淚氣體驅散示威者。<br />\n<br />\n就在Ramy Inocencio報導期間，有示威者突然送上雨傘，Ramy Inocencio用中文向他們道謝，不久再有示威者為Ramy Inocencio戴上安全頭盔。<br />\n<br />\n事後，Ramy Inocencio在個人Twitter上載影片，並說：「香港年青示威很友善。我上載此影片特意道謝。當時Randy正在拍攝，而警察發射催淚氣體正是我們身處的位置，有人強行遞上一把傘和一個頭盔，或許我永遠不會知道他們是誰，但我衷心感謝他們的照顧。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207893/%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E7%8D%B2%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%92%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%B4%88%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98-%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%94-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bcbs%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%AE%9A%E6%8F%9A%E5%B9%B4%E9%9D%92%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8B%E5%96%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F207893%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25B4%2588%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%259B%2594-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258Bcbs%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2596%2584%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtW